### Teste de Verificação do Webhook (GET) - Meta Business Manager
### Este é o endpoint que a Meta usa para validar seu webhook
GET https://h.coopedu.com.br/api/webhooks/whatsapp?hub.mode=subscribe&hub.verify_token=coopedu_whatsapp_secret_2025&hub.challenge=test_challenge_123
Accept: text/plain

### Resposta esperada: "test_challenge_123"

###

### Teste de Recebimento de Mensagem de Texto (POST)
POST https://h.coopedu.com.br/api/webhooks/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "object": "whatsapp_business_account",
  "entry": [
    {
      "id": "BUSINESS_ACCOUNT_ID",
      "changes": [
        {
          "value": {
            "messaging_product": "whatsapp",
            "metadata": {
              "display_phone_number": "5511999999999",
              "phone_number_id": "123456789012345"
            },
            "contacts": [
              {
                "profile": {
                  "name": "Ricardo Teste"
                },
                "wa_id": "5511988888888"
              }
            ],
            "messages": [
              {
                "from": "5511988888888",
                "id": "wamid.test123456",
                "timestamp": "1737395000",
                "text": {
                  "body": "Olá, preciso de ajuda com meu atendimento!"
                },
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          },
          "field": "messages"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

