### Teste Local (Development)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/webhooks/whatsapp?hub.mode=subscribe&hub.verify_token=coopedu_whatsapp_secret_2025&hub.challenge=local_test_456
Accept: text/plain

###

### Teste Local de Mensagem
